  <name>eRadio</name>
  <summary>A minimalist and powerful radio player</summary>
  <description>
    <p>eRadio is a radio player with native desktop features such as: Sound indicator integration, Media Keys Support, Notifications.</p>
    <p>It support many stream types including m3u, pls, asx and has a webradio URI scheme to easily add new stations from your internet browser</p>
    <p>You can also backup and import radio stations via erpkg files</p>
  </description>
